                <h2>ğŸ“Š ë°œí‘œ ì´ë ¥</h2>
                <div class="history-section">
                    <button class="btn-danger" onclick="clearHistory()" style="margin-bottom: 15px;">ì´ë ¥ ì´ˆê¸°í™”</button>
